N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1271.23 - Permission to cross highway under aircraft's own power required

State Regulations

No aircraft shall cross an air terminal highway or a
public highway at the air terminal under its own power without
permission. Notes
